headline: IDEX Corporation to Webcast Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Call
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., October 10, 2025--IDEX Corp. (NYSE:IEX) will release third quarter 2025 results October 29, 2025, prior to market open. Investor call scheduled for 8:00 a.m. CT.
